<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:08:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>为什么韩国数千名初级医生罢工，这对患者意味着什么</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-thousands-of-junior-doctors-in-south-korea-are-striking-and-what-it-means-for-patients/articleshow/108058486.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108058486.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国数千名初级医生举行罢工，抗议政府招收更多医学生的计划。罢工造成医院中断，并威胁到整体医疗服务。政府已为医生重返工作岗位设定了最后期限，否则将面临吊销执照和法律后果。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-thousands-of-junior-doctors-in-south-korea-are-striking-and-what-it-means-for-patients/articleshow/108058486.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国再次打破全球生育率最低记录</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-shatters-record-for-worlds-lowest-fertility-rate-yet-again/articleshow/108058090.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108058090.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着韩国人口老龄化的影响日益显现，韩国创下了世界最低生育率的新纪录。缺乏婴儿正在加速韩国社会的老龄化，引发人们对公共养老金和医疗保健财政负担日益沉重的担忧。婴儿数量减少也意味着韩国士兵数量减少，这给国家安全蒙上了长长的阴影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-shatters-record-for-worlds-lowest-fertility-rate-yet-again/articleshow/108058090.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日利亚工会工人因通货膨胀飙升和未兑现承诺而在全国范围内举行罢工</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigerias-union-workers-are-on-strike-nationwide-over-soaring-inflation-and-unmet-promises/articleshow/108057194.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108057194.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于通胀飙升和总统博拉·蒂努布政策造成的经济痛苦，尼日利亚政府雇员和工会工人举行罢工。尽管承诺提供援助和增加工资，但骚乱仍在持续。大多数服务仍在继续，但劳动力有所减少。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigerias-union-workers-are-on-strike-nationwide-over-soaring-inflation-and-unmet-promises/articleshow/108057194.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在密歇根州共和党总统初选中击败黑莉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-defeats-nikki-haley-in-michigan-republican-primary/articleshow/108056982.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108056982.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在密歇根州共和党初选中获胜，继续在多个州击败对手尼基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 的势头。尼基·黑莉在竞选期间批评特朗普，但仍致力于总统竞选。民主党方面，总统乔·拜登赢得了密歇根州初选，为可能在 2024 年白宫竞选中与特朗普重赛奠定了基础。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:48:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-defeats-nikki-haley-in-michigan-republican-primary/articleshow/108056982.cms</guid></item><item><title>旧金山就数十年来的种族主义政策向黑人居民道歉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/san-francisco-apologizes-to-black-residents-for-decades-of-racist-policies/articleshow/108057060.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108057060.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;旧金山监管人员就种族歧视和歧视的延续向非裔美国人道歉，承认存在系统性和结构性歧视、暴力和暴行。这是迈向赔偿、解决财产红线、无家可归和种族贫富差距问题的重要一步。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/san-francisco-apologizes-to-black-residents-for-decades-of-racist-policies/articleshow/108057060.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登和特朗普赢得密歇根州初选，距离重赛越来越近</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-and-trump-win-michigan-primaries-setting-stage-for-rematch/articleshow/108056669.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108056669.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;密歇根州有望成为即将于 11 月 5 日举行的美国总统选举的关键战场。凭借其摇摆州的地位，密歇根州的投票可能对两党都至关重要。在2020年的选举中，拜登在该州仅以2.8个百分点的微弱优势击败特朗普，凸显了其影响整体选举结果的潜力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:30:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-and-trump-win-michigan-primaries-setting-stage-for-rematch/articleshow/108056669.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦法院起诉伊姆兰及其妻子贪污土地案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-court-indicts-imran-his-wife-in-land-graft-case/articleshow/108055811.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108055811.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦反腐败法院在卡迪尔信托案中起诉伊姆兰·汗和他的妻子布什拉·比比。他们被指控为一所教育机构获取现金和土地，以换取滥用资金的法律保障。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-court-indicts-imran-his-wife-in-land-graft-case/articleshow/108055811.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯政治犯的生活：“孤立、食物匮乏和任意惩罚”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/life-for-russian-political-prisoners-isolation-poor-food-arbitrary-punishment/articleshow/108052677.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108052677.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 19:39:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/life-for-russian-political-prisoners-isolation-poor-food-arbitrary-punishment/articleshow/108052677.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登试图扭转特朗普局面：“大约和我一样大”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-turns-tables-on-trump-about-as-old-as-i-am/articleshow/108052625.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108052625.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 19:25:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-turns-tables-on-trump-about-as-old-as-i-am/articleshow/108052625.cms</guid></item><item><title>捐赠 10 亿美元后，纽约医学院取消学费</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/new-york-medical-school-scraps-fees-after-1-bn-donation/articleshow/108052012.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108052012.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦医学院的上级组织在一份声明中表示，纽约一所医学院在收到一位富有的捐助者提供的价值 10 亿美元的“变革性礼物”后将取消学费。 “阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦医学院收到了爱因斯坦董事会主席兼蒙特菲奥里卫生系统董事会成员露丝·L·戈特斯曼教育学博士的一份变革性礼物，”该组织在周一晚间的一份声明中表示。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 18:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/new-york-medical-school-scraps-fees-after-1-bn-donation/articleshow/108052012.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯法院判处资深活动家奥尔洛夫 2.5 年监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-court-jails-veteran-activist-orlov-for-2-5-years/articleshow/108045617.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108045617.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯一家法院周二判处高级人权活动家奥列格·奥尔洛夫两年半监禁，罪名是谴责俄罗斯对乌克兰的袭击。法官说：“法院已判定奥尔洛夫有罪，并下令在总政权流放地判处两年零六个月的刑期。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 12:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-court-jails-veteran-activist-orlov-for-2-5-years/articleshow/108045617.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度 bizman 捐赠 2.25 卢比用于释放 900 名囚犯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/as-pre-ramzan-gesture-indian-businessman-donates-rs-2-25-crore-for-release-of-900-prisoners/articleshow/108044460.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108044460.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总部位于迪拜的印度商人 Firoz Merchant of Pure Gold 捐赠 22.5 亿卢比，用于释放阿拉伯国家迪拜海湾监狱中的 900 名囚犯。由麦钱特发起的“被遗忘的社会”倡议已确保 20,000 名囚犯获释。穆罕默德·优素福·马特罗希上校赞扬了麦钱特的努力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:35:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/as-pre-ramzan-gesture-indian-businessman-donates-rs-2-25-crore-for-release-of-900-prisoners/articleshow/108044460.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本提议立法将更多信息列为机密</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-proposes-law-to-classify-more-information-as-confidential/articleshow/108043867.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108043867.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本政府已提议立法扩大机密信息的分类范围，并要求对有权访问该信息的公司员工进行安全检查。然而，反对派议员担心这些新规则可能会侵犯公民自由。日本首相岸田文雄政府认为，日本与西方政府结盟将有助于与国内企业和国际盟友更好地共享信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-proposes-law-to-classify-more-information-as-confidential/articleshow/108043867.cms</guid></item><item><title>纳瓦尔尼的盟友敦促俄罗斯人参加选举日抗议活动以纪念他，这引起了克里姆林宫的愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/navalny-ally-urges-russians-to-join-election-day-protest-in-his-memory-drawing-kremlin-ire/articleshow/108042638.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108042638.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;已故反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的亲密盟友敦促俄罗斯人按照纳瓦尔尼生前的呼吁参加下个月针对总统弗拉基米尔·普京的抗议活动。克里姆林宫警告说，那些支持这一“挑衅性呼吁”的人将面临法律后果，克里姆林宫指责这些人是美国支持的危险极端分子。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:34:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/navalny-ally-urges-russians-to-join-election-day-protest-in-his-memory-drawing-kremlin-ire/articleshow/108042638.cms</guid></item><item><title>米尼塔·桑格维 (Minita Sanghvi) 获得民主党正式提名，她可能成为纽约州参议院第一位女同性恋者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/minita-sanghvi-who-could-be-first-gay-woman-in-ny-senate-gets-official-democratic-nomination/articleshow/108042188.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108042188.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度裔美国人米尼塔·桑格维 (Minita Sanghvi) 获得纽约州第 44 州参议院选区的民主党提名。她得到了萨拉托加县民主委员会和斯克内克塔迪县民主委员会的支持。桑维是斯基德莫尔学院的营销学教授，此前曾在沃尔玛工作。她得到了印第安裔美国人影响力的支持，并将成为纽约参议院第一位公开同性恋的女性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/minita-sanghvi-who-could-be-first-gay-woman-in-ny-senate-gets-official-democratic-nomination/articleshow/108042188.cms</guid></item><item><title>几内亚与全国罢工有关的骚乱造成两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-killed-in-guinea-unrest-linked-to-nationwide-strike/articleshow/108041301.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108041301.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，几内亚首都科纳克里郊区发生全国性罢工，导致该市瘫痪并扰乱了一些采矿作业，造成两人死亡。由多个工会组成的伞式组织领导的罢工预计将继续下去。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 09:56:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-killed-in-guinea-unrest-linked-to-nationwide-strike/articleshow/108041301.cms</guid></item><item><title>“在未通知预留席位的情况下不得召开集会”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/no-assembly-session-can-be-called-without-notifying-reserved-seats-says-imran-khans-party/articleshow/108039612.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108039612.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗领导的政党声称，在召集旁遮普省和信德省议会以及首席部长宣誓就职的第二天，在没有首先宣布保留席位的情况下，不得召开省级议会会议。议会应在通知所​​有众议院议员后召开。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 09:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/no-assembly-session-can-be-called-without-notifying-reserved-seats-says-imran-khans-party/articleshow/108039612.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争：普京重组俄罗斯武装部队</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-war-putin-restructures-russian-armed-forces/articleshow/108034496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108034496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 07:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-war-putin-restructures-russian-armed-forces/articleshow/108034496.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京盟友承认俄罗斯对中国的依赖日益加深</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-admits-russias-growing-dependency-on-china/articleshow/108031312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108031312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于乌克兰冲突相关制裁，俄罗斯与西方的关系逐渐疏远，俄罗斯与中国的贸易大幅增加。自2014年吞并克里米亚以来，获得人民币贷款的努力有所加强，但进展仍然有限。尽管寻求中国资本来弥补西方制裁的缺口，但财政部长安东·西卢阿诺夫承认，达成协议仍然遥不可及。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-admits-russias-growing-dependency-on-china/articleshow/108031312.cms</guid></item><item><title>漏油事件给伊拉克农民带来压力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers/articleshow/108030892.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108030892.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊拉克拥有巨大的石油财富，但北部许多贫困的农民表示，原油泄漏污染了他们的土地，给他们已经在与干旱作斗争的压力雪上加霜。伊拉克饱受数十年冲突、腐败和基础设施破败的蹂躏，石油泄漏污染了北部省份的农田，尤其是在冬季降雨期间。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers/articleshow/108030892.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>